VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT readOnlyRootFilesystem\s*:\s*false
WHEN EXPR MISSING:readOnlyRootFilesystem:\s*true|emptyDir|tmpfs:|volumeMounts && PRESENT:kind:\s*Deployment|kind:\s*StatefulSet|kind:\s*DaemonSet|kind:\s*Pod
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects containers with a writable root filesystem.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Read-Only Root Filesystem Not Enforced.
